Summary[edit]

Tetun: Bandeira Timór Lorosa'e nian
Português: Bandeira de Timor-Leste
العربية: علم تيمور الشرقية
Deutsch: Flagge Osttimors
English: Flag of Timor-Leste (East Timor)
Bahasa Indonesia: Bendera Timor Leste
Italiano: Bandiera di Timor Est
Nederlands: Vlag van Timor-Leste (Oost-Timor)
Русский: Флаг Восточного Тимора

Source: Drawn by User:SKopp

Colours: Pantone 485C for red, 123C for yellow (source: http://www.flag.de/FOTW/flags/tl'uno.html, conversion to RGB in Photoshop)
